.howto
  %h2 First
  %pre $ gem install memprof

  %h2 Then, in your application to be profiled (before anything else)
  %pre require `gem which memprof/signal`

  %h2 Finally
  %pre=h "$ memprof --pid <pid> --name <dump name> --key #{logged_in? ? current_user['api_key'] : '<api key>'}"

